title: Kristopher Woods, Two Bedroom Townhome
posting_body: ['re you looking for a new home?', 'Come discover Kristopher Woods Apartments.', 'Located in Clarkston, Kristopher Woods is bound to offer you an incredible location and living experience.', 'Spacious bedrooms, and accommodating kitchens with electric appliances are just a few of the luxuries you will find when you enter your new home!', 'Our community also offers a laundry facility and a mail center for your convenience.', 'Location is everything and living in Kristopher Woods you will find yourself just minutes away from I-285, excellent schools, Stone Mountain Park and Northlake.', 'If you are interested in making this beautiful community your home, contact us today for more information!', 'Two Bedroom Townhome - $1195.00 (Available after October 14th, 2022)', '• Water, Trash, and Pest Control included in total.', 'Resident is responsible for activating power in their unit upon approval.', 'Prerequisites:', '• Income 3x the rent or more.', '• No Evictions, Collections, Felonies, or Bankruptcies on the background and credit check.', '• Credit Score Minimum of 550 or higher.', 'Application Process: Please call for more information.', 'Community Amenities that you will enjoy while living at Kristopher Woods:', '*24hrs.', 'Emergency Maintenance.', '*Excellent Clarkston location.', '*Playground Area.', '*Tennis court.', 'Stop by or feel free to call at', 'show contact info', '*Kristopher Woods Apartments*', '792 Jolly Avenue South', 'Clarkston, GA 30021', 'Monday-Friday between 9am to 5pm', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change at anytime*', '<URL>']
